title: ‘Arsene Wenger WILL sign a new contract extension at Arsenal despite fans fury over lack of Premier League titles’, insists former defender Martin Keown
text:
EFL 'arsene staying' ‘Arsene Wenger WILL sign a new contract extension at Arsenal despite fans fury over lack of Premier League titles’, insists former defender Martin Keown 
Ex-Gunners stalwart insists Frenchman will be master of his own fate and it is question of when new deal will be finalised By ANDREW RICHARDSON
